Complete restructuring from flat lattice_ref/ to proper src/lattice/ package layout.

Key changes:
- Migrated to src/ layout with pyproject.toml (PEP 517/518)
- Added comprehensive test suite (300 passing tests)
- New modules: crypto, bundle_signing, decision_tree_engine,
  tripwire_framework, tripwire_trace_contract, multi_cell coordination
- Added JSON schemas for all core data structures
- Critical infrastructure examples with policy bundles and audit traces
- Governance engine matrix, TOCTOU execution gate, and audit chain tests
- Removed legacy lattice_ref/, spec/, test_vectors/ directories
